ose the perfect bedding essentials.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-faUpoM jULbDz pf-85_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-86_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-edERGn cHFtyQ pf-87_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-89_">The Mattress</span></h2><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-tAExr jSVzEc pf-90_"></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-tAExr jSVzEc pf-93_ pf-lg-hide pf-hide"></div><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-96_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-98_">Sleeping on a <a href="/products/emma-original-mattress" target="_self">high-quality mattress</a>, and personalised according to our needs, is very important to have an excellent quality of sleep. It has been confirmed that there are very frequent musculoskeletal problems that are nowadays related to the use of a bad mattress.<br><br>Here’s how you can recognise a good mattress:
<br><br>• The best mattress should try to relax all the muscle tension as much as possible, reduce the stress accumulated during the day, and help you start the day full of energy.<br><br>• An uncomfortable, too rigid, or on the contrary, excessively soft surface does not allow the body to relax. As a result, you would end up tossing and turning in bed for the whole night.<br><br>If you wake up with the feeling of not getting enough rest or you are sleeping badly, maybe it’s time to change your old mattress.
